<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l27"><expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> Sebachs <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vnd des francʒen funkeln ewrs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l28">dieners <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l29">ervvirdıkeit cʒuvviſſen / daʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu der cʒeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l30">niht anheim iſt / vnd <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> der herheim kümt Jſt <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l31">der vns von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wegen daran mant / ſo <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir Jn </ab>
